{"url": "www.popsugar.com/celebrity/photo-gallery/44106786/embed/44106865/Lindsay-Jill-Roth-BFF", "text": "Meghan Markle and Prince Harry's long-awaited Netflix docuseries, \"Harry & Meghan,\" debuted its final episodes on Dec. 15. The documentary event features not only interviews with the titular couple but also never-before-seen photos and footage of their life together, starting from when they first dated. The crew also spoke to some of their loved ones, including Markle's mother, Doria Ragland; her niece, Ashleigh Hale; and many of her friends who've stood by her side for years. Some of the friends featured include her \"Suits\" costar Abigail Spencer and her college friend Lindsay Jill Roth.\n\nMarkle, who worked in Hollywood for years before she met Harry, cultivated her own group of successful friends long before she met her future husband in 2016. That includes Priyanka Chopra, tennis superstar Serena Williams, and many of her \"Suits\" cast mates. She also forged a bond with Sophie Gr\u00e9goire Trudeau, whose husband is now the prime minister of Canada. And after she and Harry became an item, she became very close to George and Amal Clooney, as well as Hollywood mogul Tyler Perry.\n\nRead ahead to see all of Markle's most famous friends and what we know about their relationships.", "images": ["https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/hOXLfsEP4EW10nstKw5tJ_gatUg=/fit-in/792x531/top/filters:format_auto():upscale()/2019/02/20/671/n/1922398/f69fdbb75c6d6ce9bee852.62707299_GettyImages-961544566.jpg", "https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/7RXnfy0AjoYFcAjSUn1wMq4wJ-M=/fit-in/792x1188/filters:format_auto():upscale()/2019/02/20/671/n/1922398/560879b45c6d6ce81e5386.92295636_GettyImages-478276162.jpg", "https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/IO3uDA5B-RARFPZpYG7PXD_mDyw=/2138x0:7602x5464/116x116/filters:format_auto():extract_cover()/2025/09/22/935/n/49351763/1991c7aa68d1bf20201491.00280764_.jpg", "https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files